  • Smart bulbs that work with Alexa: Select Frustration Free Setup at checkout to have your device automatically paired with your Amazon Alexa device when it arrives.
  • Easy connection: Easily connect these smart light bulbs directly to your Wi-Fi router, providing voice control for your Cync and C by GE smart bulbs through voice assistants (sold separately) and control away from home - no hub or bridge required.
  • Manage your smart bulbs away from home: Get added home security and convenience by controlling your Wi-Fi light bulbs with the Cync mobile app. With these Cync smart lights, never come home to a dark house or disrupt your comfort from bed.
  • Smart lights with adjustable white temperature: These smart light bulbs allow you to adjust white light to any color temperature between warm, amber light (2000K) and cool, bluish tones (7000K), including settings optimized for your sleep/wake cycle.
  • LED smart bulbs: These smart lights fit medium base sockets for 60W incandescent A19 bulbs, helping make your house a smart home. These smart LED light bulbs use 84% less energy and last 15 times longer than a 60W incandescent bulbs.

Additional details

Smart bulbs that work with Alexa: Select Frustration Free Setup at checkout to have your device automatically paired with your Amazon Alexa device when it arrives. Easy connection: Easily connect these smart light bulbs directly to your Wi-Fi router, providing voice control for your Cync and C by GE smart bulbs through voice assistants (sold separately) and control away from home, no hub or bridge required. Manage your smart bulbs away from home: Get added home security and convenience by controlling your Wi-Fi light bulbs with the Cync mobile app. With these Cync smart lights, never come home to a dark house or disrupt your comfort from bed. Smart lights with adjustable white temperature: These smart light bulbs allow you to adjust white light to any color temperature between warm, amber light (2000K) and cool, bluish tones (7000K), including settings optimized for your sleep/wake cycle. LED smart bulbs: These smart lights fit medium base sockets for 60W incandescent A19 bulbs, helping make your house a smart home. These smart LED light bulbs use 84% less energy and last 15 times longer than a 60W incandescent bulbs.

    I like the CSYNC app (Android, I have not tried Apple version). It works well, so far. It can group so that a light with two of these bulbs can work together. Brightness range is good. It can be set as dim as a candle. These have color adjustment from dull orange to blue-white, (color temperature, NOT full RGB range).

    After these light bulbs were setup and working with CSYNC app, i tried to connect Alexa. This did not go smoothly. I needed to do factory reset on the lights and re-do the setup with Alexa. I expected the CSYNC skill in Alexa to work like the CSYNC app, but groups are different, light controls are different. Alexa allows five color temperature settings instead of the 0-100 slider in the CSYNC app.

    After these light bulbs were setup and working with Alexa, I tried to go back in with the CSYNC app to fine-tune the color. The CSYNC app did not connect. Add device in CSYNC fails. it looks like Alexa setup locks out the CSYNC app. Can't have both. I will leave Alexa in control.
